{
  "texts": [
    "Our proposed method has several challenges for improvement.",
    "These include investigation on how to use suggestive endings, questioning, and definitive explanations depending on situations and laboratory studies to understand the cognitive processes during decision-making tasks using our chatbot strategy.",
    "However, we believe that suggestive endings in chatbot answers constitute a good strategy for AI-powered chatbots to enhance critical information seeking and decision-making.",
    "Frontiers in Psychology frontiersin.org",
    "Amazon Mechanical Turk: https://www.mturk.com/."
  ]
}